parameters.name: DQF
parameters.description: Array of SPC data quality indicators.

parameters.name: general_flag
parameters.description: Global quality flag, signifying whether the data for this epoch are suitable for use without caveate.

parameters.name: vp_moment_SC_gd
parameters.description: Proton bulk velocity from the 1st moment of the reduced distribution function, in the spacecraft frame (Only Good Quality)

parameters.name: vp_moment_RTN_gd
parameters.description: Proton bulk velocity from the 1st moment of the reduced distribution function in [inertial] RTN coordinate system (Only Good Quality)

parameters.name: np_moment_gd
parameters.description: Proton density estimate from the 0th moment of the reduced distribution function (Only Good Quality)

parameters.name: wp_moment_gd
parameters.description: Proton radial [most probable] thermal speed estimate from the 2nd velocity moment of the reduced distribution function (Only Good Quality)
